  "format": "The Coens' slot on the century list, and Sean and Amanda hand it to No. 15 instead of the obvious pick. A conversation about 'Inside Llewyn Davis,' the 1961-set folk portrait modeled on Dave Van Ronk and the movie about being the other guy, and why 'A Complete Unknown' plays like a response record a decade later.",
